body.description: Stuck between a stink and a tight space? No worries! Febreze Small Spaces air fresheners are now longer lasting, for up to 45 days. So, they're the perfect, all-in-one odor fighter for all those tiny spots you forget need to be freshened up: We're talkin' bathrooms, closets, the corner where your cat's litter box lives, and more. Just press firmly to activate, then set one down wherever you want continuous freshness... it'll keep fighting those small-room stinks for 45 days. With 2X the Odor-Fighting power (vs. base Febreze), Heavy Duty Pet Odor Fighter keeps your life fresh... even when it gets a little ruff. Want to keep hitting refresh around your home? Give other scents a try and keep spreading that fresh joy around.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Loved the gentle fragrance!
reviews.reviewText: This has been a lifesaver for maintaining a fresh and inviting atmosphere in my home, especially with pets. The pet-friendly formula effectively eliminates odors without overpowering fragrances. Its compact design is perfect for small spaces like bathrooms, closets, or near litter boxes, ensuring a consistent and pleasant scent without being too strong. The fresh scent is subtle and not overwhelming, making it a great alternative to heavy or artificial air fresheners. I appreciate that it doesn't just mask odors but truly eliminates them, leaving my home smelling clean and welcoming. It is a reliable and pet-friendly solution for keeping your home smelling fresh and free from unwanted odors. It's a must-have for pet owners and anyone looking for a subtle and effective air freshening option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best for spaces with competing odors
reviews.reviewText: We use this for a bedroom that has poor ventilation and four dogs in it. The scent is pretty strong over time, and it's a little overpowering if it's the only scent in the room. But it's perfect if you're trying to combat smells.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Febreze small spaces work great but don't last!
reviews.reviewText: Febreze small spaces do a great job and smell awesome! However they do not last more than a day or two at the most, if they last longer than that they have a very faint smell. When you first take them out and set them up they are perfect, I usually buy the four packs for a better deal, usually the price of two singles are about the price of a four pack most places.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great at masking odors
reviews.reviewText: I think these are really great at masking odors! It only lasts a few weeks, but for the price and comparison to plug-ins it is long lasting to me. I use it by litter boxes which helps a lot and also in our living room. I would definitely buy again. I do wish they had refills so I don't have to waste plastic or used a material that is not plastic.
